responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[24F282B6434E981D3FBC5B9E3C7849C5]", "DAB8BF5B4DFE47B91C46D49BFB0A2730", "Thraen wants answers, and he\'ll get his reports. But if you find something different down in those deeps... something that speaks of a physical taint, a creeping darkness, an unnatural decay on the constructs or the very stone... I want to know. Directly. Discreetly. Flinthelm is looking for spiritual echoes; I\'m looking for a tangible plague. If you find proof of this corruption, say, a piece of a construct visibly warped by it, or a sample of ore that actively seethes with this dark energy. Bring it to me.")
name: ANV_FTUE_Dunir_BrimirColdchisel_5_Response
